hopobject.body: How much is a First Class stamp? www.suboxone-directory.com Citizen of the world - I work with a lot of people who have the mentality of the "screw you, I got mine" mentality. But guess what they're Democrats. That's right Democrats. They plan on getting the subsidies for healthcare insurance through the ACA (Obamacare) by quitting work and losing their insurance. Talk about "screwyou, I got mine". I'll be subsidizing their healthcare coverage.
